metadata.title: JARDLI Glass Lily Pipe Inflow with Surface Skimmer for Aquarium Planted Tank (20mm for 19/25mm (3/4'' i.d.) tubing)
features: Glass transparency give superb appearance to your aquarium. Make an elegant curve line in your aquarium.
Surface skimmer removes surface scum effectively. More easily and help photosynthesis of water plants.
360-degree inflow design allows water flows get through from all directions without clogging and provides convenience in cleaning.
20mm outer diameter fit the canister filter tubing of 3/4" i.d.(19/25mm). Compatible with Eheim, Tetra and other filters.
Package included: 1x glass lily pipe surface skimmer inflow, 2x suction cups.
description: The inflow pipe carries water from the aquarium down to the canister filter. The inflow pipes suitable for all type of external canister filter.  Easy to clean, remove convenient assembly.
well made, would not hurt fish and shrimp. The surface skimmer efficiently skims dissolved organics and other waste material from the water’s surface of your aquarium.
Removable, rotate around to adjust flow. 360-degree intake float is positioned consistently at the surface and the ﬂow control valve enables you to increase or decrease flow rate to your filter.
Give superb appearance to your aquarium.
13mm for 12/16mm (1/2'' id) water tube 17mm for 16/22mm (5/8'' id) water tube 20mm for 19/25mm (3/4'' id) water tube
1x lily pipe inflow with skimmer 2x suction cups
